Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:14.93,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:15.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.83,0:00:18.91,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:23.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:26.79,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:30.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.45,0:00:34.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:36.84,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.77,0:00:40.30,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:45.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:48.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:51.20,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.31,0:00:54.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:00:59.54,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:03.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.53,0:01:11.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:15.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.14,0:01:18.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,160.389)}Lightning Monster Eiking's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs126\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,650.389)}Worldwide Blackout Operation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.56,0:01:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like someone's following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.47,0:01:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Akemi Seki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who's there? Who's calling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.56,0:01:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Akemi, speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.41,0:02:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is your father, Doctor Seki, hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.50,0:02:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My father went missing two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Seki has escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.47,0:02:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He escaped to see you, his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.62,0:02:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My father escaped?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean... he's alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.89,0:02:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.81,0:02:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.98,0:02:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.51,0:02:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- What is it?\N- Let's check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw Eiking, did you? Foolish humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.37,0:02:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Crash, lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He will come...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He will come to see his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when I'll strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let her go until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, sorry. I totally overslept.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been walking around\Nfor three days straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone would be exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure I picked up mystery waves within a\Nten kilometers radius of these mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the FBI's detectors\Ncan malfunction now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.31,0:03:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll go gather firewood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.85,0:03:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.97,0:03:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.71,0:04:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.65,0:04:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't order me around any longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is somebody after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Shocker's dogs...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's dogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're after Shocker ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We're fighting against Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.73,0:04:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Akemi... I'll finally get to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki. You think he's a Shocker runaway?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Colonel Zol?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You still haven't caught\Nthe runaway Doctor Seki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The runaway doctor will\Nsurely go to see his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a network set up around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time\Nbefore we bring him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Seki is Eiking's creator.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to build more Eikings,\Nand use them to take out generators
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world's greatest\Ncities, beginning with Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Worldwide Blackout Operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We need Doctor Seki to make it happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It was I who came up with that plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm well aware of Doctor Seki's importance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Zol.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We got an emergency message\Nfrom the third patrol team.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Tire marks were found at 13 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Put them on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The tracks were left by two motorbikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.82,0:05:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Could Ichimonji Hayato and that\NFBI agent have found Doctor Seki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Akemi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.31,0:06:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He's awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.67,0:06:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're safe now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.63,0:06:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Where... Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We brought you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Did you?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.87,0:06:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've escaped Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind, we'd like\Nto hear what happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Toshihiko Seki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My specialty is marine biology.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And Shocker forced you to work\Non their team of scientists?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned of their terrifying\Nworld conquest ambitions,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and spent two years waiting to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.23,0:06:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My! Two whole years?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That must have been hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't even stand one day like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.01,0:07:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I can't stay here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to show Akemi that I'm safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.33,0:07:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even walk in your condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides that, Doctor, Shocker is clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll know you plan to see your daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and they may have prepared an ambush.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.46,0:07:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing them, it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But I... I want to see Akemi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.37,0:07:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the only thing that\Nkept me going all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.54,0:07:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring your daughter to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.73,0:07:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You will?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.17,0:07:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he's very trustworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can leave it in his hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.87,0:07:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.72,0:07:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for Ichimonji Hayato\Nto show his stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you forgetting someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What, are you going too, Mr. Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:08:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think you'll just slow him down?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.27,0:08:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:15.12,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an9\c&H000000&\3c&H384E63&\fs60}Seki Marine Biology Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:13.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Seki Marine Biology Institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You think Akemi's safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That monster said my father was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.82,0:08:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's true...\NI'm sure he'll come to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.54,0:08:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.31,0:08:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, come home safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:08:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- I just heard a scream!\N- It came from inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.97,0:09:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You handle things here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker cyborg...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.54,0:09:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Eiking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you're here makes\NDoctor Seki's whereabouts obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll be taking his daughter\Nas a hostage in his place!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.45,0:09:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you take Akemi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Crash, lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.83,0:09:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider...\Nyou've shown yourself at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.81,0:10:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Eiking... If you know what's good for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll put the girl down\Nand get out of my sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.17,0:10:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It is I, Eiking, who shall defeat you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,so that you can never\Ninterfere with us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you'll see Eiking's true power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold, the power of a\Nmillion volts of electricity!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.31,0:10:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Crash, lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:10:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the power of Eiking!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider is no match for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.84,0:11:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He got me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.75,0:11:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the doctor's daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.46,0:11:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker has her...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean you messed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a formidable foe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:34.71,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't apologize enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.73,0:11:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They've taken Akemi hostage, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.57,0:11:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you come back\Nafter letting that happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you go after him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.38,0:11:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you risk your\Nlife to protect her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to keep your head...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato did everything he could.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:11:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being too cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Hayato messes up sometimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.55,0:12:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato can't afford to fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the nature of\NIchimonji Hayato's mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And if he dies...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.26,0:12:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,it's all down the drain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would fight Shocker then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So are you! And Mari, and Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Goro can fight when he has to!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.82,0:12:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll all fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I may have been too\Nfocused on saving myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A man focused only on saving himself\Ncan't also risk his life to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please, stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see my presence has caused\Nyou a great deal of trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.98,0:12:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I shouldn't have escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor. I promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring your daughter\Nback if it kills me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.16,0:13:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll have her back in their base by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They're probably torturing her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a strong-willed girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.46,0:13:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You still refuse to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten more minutes under these lights,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and your face will be\Nburned beyond recognition!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.04,0:13:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather die than talk, if it means bringing\Nmy father back to this awful place...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I love my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Love him, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.63,0:13:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The love of father and child?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.26,0:13:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you love him that much,\Nsurely you don't want him to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.02,0:13:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Under Shocker law, if your\Nfather does not return to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.96,0:13:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,we will have to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.23,0:13:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That death will be at the hand\Nof his own creation, Eiking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to kill my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to let your beloved father die?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Or will you do as I say and speak to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll speak to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.36,0:14:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, I ended up creating\Nthat ray cyborg, Eiking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is Shocker's endgame, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.11,0:14:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What destruction do they\Nmean to cause with Eiking?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Eiking's body contains over\None million volts of electricity...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.63,0:14:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? Tachibana Racing Club...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is Akemi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Akemi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.21,0:14:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Akemi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.53,0:14:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please let me speak to my father.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She only wants to speak to the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll speak to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.73,0:14:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.35,0:14:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Akemi... are you safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on. Tell him to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.35,0:15:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Father... Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.93,0:15:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of there!\NShocker's coming to kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Seki. If you want to save\Nyour beloved daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,come to Ikuta Apartment Complex alone,\Ntomorrow morning at ten o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A car will come to fetch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If you come back peacefully,\Nwithout revealing any information,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll overlook your escape\Nand ensure your daughter's safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.40,0:15:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're not lying?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a man who keeps his promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.25,0:15:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen... just don't say a word\Nto compromise our plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.47,0:15:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.37,0:15:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.41,0:15:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Zol...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Zol! Colonel Zol!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What did your daughter say, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they threaten to kill your\Ndaughter if you didn't return to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.27,0:16:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like their usual MO.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.43,0:16:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's absolutely horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.71,0:16:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.26,0:16:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... give me some time alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.47,0:16:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I can say right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give him time alone, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.63,0:16:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.26,0:16:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let my daughter be killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.60,0:16:55.72,Italics,,0,0,0,,Come to Ikuta Apartment Complex alone,\Ntomorrow morning at ten o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A car will come to fetch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for all your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.09,0:17:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.98,0:17:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait until he meets his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.11,0:17:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Let's tail them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is my daughter? Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.25,0:17:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're taking you to meet her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be patient until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the way to the power station.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.67,0:18:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The million-volt station\Nthat powers over ten cities?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I see now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,See what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.48,0:18:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What Shocker is using Eiking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,When I flip this switch, it will detonate\Nall of the bombs we've placed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.21,0:18:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If we blow up this power station,\Nit will blackout ten whole cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Shocker will spring into action,\Nand conquer those cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.22,0:18:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Where... Where is my daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.77,0:19:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Seki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Eiking... don't tell me, Akemi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We're about to kick off\NWorldwide Blackout Operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.53,0:19:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll kill her in the\Nfilthy traitor's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.19,0:19:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Look up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.35,0:19:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Akemi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.25,0:19:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Father! Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No! This wasn't the agreement!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.79,0:19:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Father... why? Why didn't you run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Akemi... please, spare her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.18,0:19:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We need you to create more Eikings!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Akemi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.99,0:19:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Akemi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let him escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Ichimonji Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, go save your daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Eiking... I won't let you\Ndestroy this power station!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.02,0:20:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll blow you up with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Detonation team, hit the switch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.41,0:20:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Eiking?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.49,0:20:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Eiking is outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.21,0:21:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't escape, Eiking!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.58,0:21:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll finish what I started last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.50,0:21:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.31,0:21:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's taking you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.83,0:22:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider... It's time we finished this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Crash, lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.12,0:22:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I need to take the\Nchance, even if it kills me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.50,0:22:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.32,0:22:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.02,0:22:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.87,0:23:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.63,0:23:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Today you taught me the power\Nthat love and trust can inspire.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.04,0:23:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Mr. Tachibana will be happy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.31,0:23:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.09,0:23:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad the power station made it\Nout with just some minor damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.95,0:23:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.68,0:23:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shake a leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.97,0:23:30.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They managed to prevent Shocker's\NWorldwide Blackout Operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.03,0:23:33.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But enemies more powerful than\NEiking might still lie in store.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.07,0:23:36.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Go, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.06,0:23:40.58,Cont,,0,40,150,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.15,0:23:43.06,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.15,0:23:45.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.07,0:23:46.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monstrous Wolf Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.49,0:23:50.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A creepy masked party\Nunfolds on Christmas night.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.37,0:23:52.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Colonel Zol risks his\Nlife on Operation: Wolf,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.53,0:23:55.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and Taki Kazuya and Ichimonji\NHayato bravely stand to face him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.79,0:24:01.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for "The\NMonstrous Wolf Man's Killer Party!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.10,0:24:01.10,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\fscy85\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,220.389)}The Monstrous Wolf Man's
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.10,0:24:01.10,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs175\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(517.167,680.389)}Killer Party
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.04,0:24:09.88,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.46,0:24:12.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.46,0:24:14.42,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.42,0:24:17.47,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the villains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.97,0:24:19.84,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.84,0:24:21.72,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.72,0:24:23.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.51,0:24:24.96,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.31,0:24:27.23,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.40,0:24:33.07,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with all of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.07,0:24:36.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.69,0:24:40.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.79,0:24:45.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Lightning Monster Eiking\NWorldwide Blackout Operation